  • java.lang.Object

    Cloneable, HTMLDOMElement, HTMLDOMNode

    public class JsoupHTMLDOMElement
extends JsoupHTMLDOMNode
implements HTMLDOMElement
    The JsoupHTMLDOMElement class is official implementation of HTMLDOMElement for the Jsoup library.
